1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:58,359 --> 00:01:00,000
You are all accomplices
of Lord of Zhenbei

4
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,880
(Dongshi Gate)
and His Lordship's rebel forces.

5
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,320
At noon each day,

6
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,640
one will be executed.

7
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,319
Execute!

8
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:16,719
Stop!

9
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,200
You came.

10
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,919
I warned you before.

11
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:11,280
No man can be trusted.

12
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,240
Look, I only killed a few,

13
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,960
and he handed you over.

14
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:16,000
Sister.

15
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:19,240
Let those innocent officials go.

16
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:28,240
They don't want a woman in power.

17
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:32,479
Kui, why plead for them?

18
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,599
Sister.

19
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,479
You are the ruler now.

20
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:37,560
If you suppress those who disagree

21
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,560
by force,

22
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,120
how is that different

23
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,960
from when Kun invaded

24
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,879
our Zhao Tribe?

25
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,240
Shut up!

26
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,879
If Feng Ye hadn't taken you away,

27
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,319
I wouldn't have had to do this

28
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,319
to force you back.

29
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:52,080
It's all Feng Ye's fault.

30
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,599
He changed you.

31
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,639
He didn't change me.

32
00:02:58,639 --> 00:03:00,439
He showed me what I never knew.

33
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,599
I once lived in a cage,

34
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:06,240
never knowing love.

35
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:12,400
But then I met all kinds of people

36
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:16,080
and felt the warmth

37
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,360
and kindness of this world.

38
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,560
Sister.

39
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:22,000
I know

40
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:24,840
you don't want the Zhao Tribe
to be oppressed again.

41
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,800
You don't want women
to be looked down upon

42
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,159
and trampled by others.

43
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,800
That's why you fought for power.

44
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,520
But your methods are wrong.

45
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,159
Those you've killed,

46
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:43,919
they were innocent.

47
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,520
I don't care!

48
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:51,039
Kui.

49
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:54,039
In my heart,

50
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,439
besides you and me,

51
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:57,240
no one else matters.

52
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,360
Sacrificing a few

53
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,000
is nothing to me.

54
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:03,400
But they are real people!

55
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:06,000
Just like you and me!

56
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:08,400
Those fighting inside and outside
these palace walls.

57
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:11,159
They were driven to the edge by you.

58
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,599
Feng Ye just didn't want

59
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:14,560
anyone else to suffer in silence

60
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,439
like we once did.

61
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:17,879
And I'm just trying to stop you

62
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:20,000
from becoming the very thing
you hated most.

63
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,160
I can't watch you walk forward

64
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,560
on the blood of the innocent.

65
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,720
Report.

66
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:32,959
Your Majesty.

67
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,160
His Lordship has stormed the palace.

68
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,000
What about the guards and officials?

69
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,720
They...

70
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:38,839
Say it!

71
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,480
They all support Lord Nine-Thousand.

72
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,120
They say he is the late Emperor's son.

73
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,839
Then why are you afraid?

74
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,879
He is the late Emperor's son.

75
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,160
Then what about me?

76
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,199
Sister.

77
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:11,000
A mayfly is trying to shake a tree.

78
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,560
You're overreaching.

79
00:05:18,140 --> 00:05:20,220
(Diligence in Governance,
Trust in the Virtuous)

80
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,800
Lord Nine-Thousand.

81
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:34,920
You've opposed His Majesty
many times before.

82
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:37,040
Are you rebelling now?

83
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,079
Lord Nine-Thousand is the late
Emperor's surviving son.

84
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:40,959
The throne

85
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:42,120
should be his.

86
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,519
His?

87
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,040
On what grounds?

88
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,680
It's not even certain

89
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,079
if he truly is the late Emperor's son.

90
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:54,480
And even if he is,

91
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:56,000
just because he carries

92
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,399
the blood of that tyrant?

93
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:00,399
Why can't I sit on this throne

94
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,120
simply because

95
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:03,279
of my bloodline and my gender?

96
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,519
The throne

97
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:12,079
belongs to the most capable.

98
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,759
I made it this far.

99
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,600
I can hold it.

100
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:19,759
I never wanted this throne.

101
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,040
The two late emperors were cruel,

102
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,680
but your methods

103
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,439
are even harsher.

104
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,040
Without harshness,

105
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,279
how can you rule the realm?

106
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,959
Guards.

107
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,360
Guards.

108
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,199
Guards!

109
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,439
Sister.

110
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,519
Everyone

111
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:55,399
has pledged allegiance
to Lord Nine-Thousand now.

112
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,920
Stand down.

113
00:06:58,399 --> 00:07:02,199
You would betray me for a man?

114
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,040
It's not for him.

115
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:07,959
It's for you.

116
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,040
Sister.

117
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,000
Stand down.

118
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,079
Fine.

119
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,160
Then I'll kill Feng Ye.

120
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,199
Only when he's dead

121
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:20,199
will you come back to me.

122
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,840
Move aside.

123
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,360
You chose me after all.

124
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,080
Step back.

125
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,720
Sister.

126
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,279
Let go.

127
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,440
I will take you away

128
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,399
to a place

129
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:56,240
covered in camellias.

130
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,240
Just the two of us.

131
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,399
Feng Ye.

132
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:19,120
You will never

133
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:24,720
have

134
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,919
my Kui.

135
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:24,120
The flowers are blooming.

136
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,559
Yukui.

137
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,919
Don't touch me.

138
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,919
I promised my sister.

139
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,759
I'd take her to a place
where the mountains

140
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,919
are covered in flowers.

141
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:26,200
From now on,

142
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:29,840
let's never see each other again.

143
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:59,700
(Eight Years Later)

144
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:03,380
(Diligence in Governance,
Trust in the Virtuous)

145
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,080
Uncle,

146
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,039
must you truly leave?

147
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,919
I'm still young.

148
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,159
There's so much

149
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:16,159
I don't understand.

150
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:17,399
I fear

151
00:12:17,399 --> 00:12:19,399
I may not be ready for this throne.

152
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,320
Lin.

153
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:23,480
You'll wish me well, won't you?

154
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:54,140
(Taiji Hall)

155
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:03,820
(Taiji Hall)

156
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,639
Can't catch me!

157
00:13:07,639 --> 00:13:08,399
I'll protect you!

158
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:13,600
Can't catch me.

159
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,200
Can't catch me!

160
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,279
Yukui.

161
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:16,960
Come play with us!

162
00:13:20,559 --> 00:13:21,480
Sister.

163
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,600
I'm coming!

164
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,080
I came to find you.

165
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,440
I remember what you said before.

166
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,440
That we should never see each other
again in this life.

167
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,279
But this life is too long.

168
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:44,039
How could I bear not to see you?

169
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,639
We were born as birds in a cage,

170
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,279
yet neither of us believed

171
00:13:48,279 --> 00:13:49,840
the cage could hold us.

172
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,840
And I still refuse to believe

173
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,679
that all the misunderstandings
of the past

174
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,879
can keep us apart.

175
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,000
So this time,

176
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,879
I will never let go again.

177
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,720
Who are you talking to?

178
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:17,320
Why did you hold my arm?

179
00:14:40,740 --> 00:14:44,060
♪The moon sinks in the west.
The cold lamp burns low♪

180
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:47,380
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

181
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:51,500
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

182
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:57,700
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard.
Yet love and hate entwine♪

183
00:14:58,060 --> 00:15:01,460
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

184
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:05,460
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

185
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:09,780
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

186
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:13,340
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

187
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:15,660
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

188
00:15:15,660 --> 00:15:19,860
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

189
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:25,380
(The End)

190
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,980
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

191
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,900
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

192
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:48,220
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

193
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:52,340
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

194
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:57,020
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

195
00:15:57,020 --> 00:15:58,540
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

196
00:15:58,900 --> 00:16:02,300
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

197
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:06,300
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

198
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:10,620
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

199
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:14,180
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

200
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:16,500
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

201
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:20,700
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

202
00:16:21,140 --> 00:16:22,780
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

203
00:16:22,780 --> 00:16:24,300
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

204
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:27,500
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

205
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:29,820
♪In dreams, it's you♪

206
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:31,220
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

207
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:34,540
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

208
00:16:34,540 --> 00:16:37,940
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

209
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:41,500
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

210
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:44,740
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

211
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:48,180
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
